## matplotlib - before {background-color="#DEE0F3"}



::: {.cell}

````{.cell-code}
```{{python}}
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import numpy as np
x = np.random.rand(32);y = np.random.rand(32); colors = np.random.rand(32)
plt.scatter(x, y, c=colors)
plt.show()
```
````

::: {.cell-output-display}
